OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,F"I'm worried about going out" - those
OL,7,Fwere words I never expected to hear
OL,8,Ffrom my own father.
OL,10,FBut last summer as the violent anti-
OL,11,Fimmigration protests flared up around
OL,12,Fthe country, following the murder of
OL,13,Fthree little girls in Southport, I
OL,14,Fwatched this fearless retired surgeon
OL,15,Fbecome fearful for his safety.
OL,17,FOver the course of a week as the
OL,18,Fprotests spread, many of them
OL,19,Freplicated scenes from the 1970's and
OL,20,F80's, as hate and rage turned into
OL,21,Fviolence.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/16
