OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FOver the last three decades, as a
OL,7,Fjournalist, I have seen many protests
OL,8,Fand demonstrations turn into riots.
OL,9,FBut this time, it felt different, and
OL,10,Fmore menacing.
OL,12,FSeeing the images of right-wing groups
OL,13,Fand daubed graffiti telling asylum
OL,14,Fseekers being housed in hotels to "get
OL,15,Fout of England", even made me think,
OL,16,F"Am I Safe?".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
