OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FSometimes I forget that scenes like
OL,7,Fthis playing out on our screens can
OL,8,Fmake even the most secure person of
OL,9,Fcolour feel like prey that needs to go
OL,10,Finto hiding.
OL,12,FDuring that week there was a sense of
OL,13,Fdread, where and when, will the next
OL,14,Fprotest happen. Could it be on our
OL,15,Fdoorstep? Social media, as ever,
OL,16,Fplayed its part.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
