OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FThis time in spreading disinformation,
OL,7,Fwhipping up the growing anti-immigrant
OL,8,Fsentiment, into a frenzy. The violent
OL,9,Fscenes that played in parts of the
OL,10,FWest Country and elsewhere in the UK,
OL,11,Fcame as a warning sign that all is not
OL,12,Fwell.
OL,14,FFast forward a month after those
OL,15,Fviolence protests, I still sensed a
OL,16,Ffear in my father. A worry that there
OL,17,Fcould be a repeat of the racist
OL,18,Fsentiments he witnessed in the UK as a
OL,19,Fyounger man.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
