OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FWas he isolated in his worry, or were
OL,7,Fthere others like him? I found my
OL,8,Fanswer amongst the Senegalese
OL,9,Fcommunity in Bristol's Stapleton Road.
OL,11,FWe gathered a group at a community
OL,12,Fcafe for a chat, that included adults
OL,13,Fwho have been in the UK for over 20
OL,14,Fyears, and children who were born here.
OL,16,FThe conversation was for a TV piece,
OL,17,Fand what I heard was worrying.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
