OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FIn the months that followed I worked
OL,7,Fwith a team here at ITV News West
OL,8,FCountry to find an array of voices, to
OL,9,Ftake a temperature check of where
OL,10,Fthose often violent protests of 2024
OL,11,Fhave left us. Could they happen again
OL,12,Fand what needs to be done to make sure
OL,13,Fcommunities feel better heard.
OL,15,FThe process of making the programme
OL,16,Fopened my eyes to a wide array of
OL,17,Fideas and views. Not least that this
OL,18,Fis a polarising subject with no real
OL,19,Fclear cut answer.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
