OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FMy guests included a criminologist who
OL,7,Ftold me about the pain of facing
OL,8,Fracial hatred, and seeing scenes of
OL,9,Fviolence play out, like the riots of
OL,10,Fthe 80's where her uncle's shops were
OL,11,Fburned down.
OL,13,FI also heard from a self-employed
OL,14,Ftradesman who was given a two year
OL,15,Fprison sentence after he turned
OL,16,Fviolent during a anti-immigration
OL,17,Fprotest in Bristol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
