OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FAfter six months behind bars Dan Lock
OL,7,Fis out of prison on license, and
OL,8,Fsitting opposite me telling me his
OL,9,Fside of the story.
OL,11,FIt's hard not to like Dan, he's polite
OL,12,Fand pleasant, certainly not the image
OL,13,Fof a protester that many people would
OL,14,Fimagine. I'm told he's someone who has
OL,15,Fnever been in trouble or in jail. So
OL,16,Fwhat happened?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
