OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FFrom the moment we started the
OL,7,Finterview, he expressed his sorrow for
OL,8,Fturning violent during the protest
OL,9,Foutside a hotel housing asylum-seekers
OL,10,Fin Bristol.
OL,12,FHe says he retaliated after being
OL,13,Fcalled a Nazi. "So I'm a racist,'cos
OL,14,FI'm white and I'm bald?" he says,
OL,15,Fwhile also pointing to the tattoos on
OL,16,Fhis arm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
