OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FHe also tells me how he firmly
OL,7,Fbelieves in "stopping the boats" and
OL,8,Fthat the country needs to cease
OL,9,Fspending "billions on housing illegal
OL,10,Fimmigrants" all the while his
OL,11,Fgrandparents' winter fuel allowance is
OL,12,Fbeing cut.
OL,14,FAs the interview rolls on I realise
OL,15,FDan's views are going to rile some and
OL,16,Frally others. This was an echo of
OL,17,Fothers in this area and the country,
OL,18,Fwho feel they've been ignored and left
OL,19,Fbehind.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
