OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FAs part of the programme I also met
OL,7,FEric who has been waiting a staggering
OL,8,F15 years to get asylum in this country.
OL,10,FHe told me how he escaped the
OL,11,FDemocratic Republic of Congo as a
OL,12,Fteenager during a brutal civil war.
OL,14,FHe ran into hiding while his mother
OL,15,Fand father were slaughtered.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/16
