OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FFacing Eric and listening to his story
OL,7,FI'm reminded that in this long running
OL,8,Fargument about immigration, many have
OL,9,Fforgotten their humanity and the fact
OL,10,Fthat everyone has a right to feel
OL,11,Fsafe. Something that was far from the
OL,12,Fminds of those storming these hotels.
OL,14,FThe process of making Disunited
OL,15,FBritain has been a labour of love, and
OL,16,Ffear.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
