OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FI wasn't sure what answers this
OL,7,Fprocess could uncover. The possibility
OL,8,Fof a fractured nation unable to come
OL,9,Ftogether again, is frightening in
OL,10,Fitself, let alone the thought of that
OL,11,Fviolence playing out again.
OL,13,FBut this is a 30-minute journey that
OL,14,Fwill resonate with some, and disagree
OL,15,Fwith others. Although hearing those
OL,16,Fvoices that often sit opposite your
OL,17,Fown thought process is sometimes the
OL,18,Fkey to finding the answers to some
OL,19,Fvery uncomfortable questions.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
